#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn19.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn19.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 19 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 19 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Kumbhaṇḍasutta → aṇḍabharī-gāmakuṭako (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn19.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Kumbhaṇḍasutta "
msgstr "10. Pot Balls "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn19.10:1.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ kumbhaṇḍaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man with testicles as big as pots flying through the air. "

msgctxt "sn19.10:1.2"
msgid "So gacchantopi teva aṇḍe khandhe āropetvā gacchati. "
msgstr "When he was walking he had to lift his testicles on to his shoulder. "

msgctxt "sn19.10:1.3"
msgid "Nisīdantopi tesveva aṇḍesu nisīdati. "
msgstr "And when he sat down, he sat right on them. "

msgctxt "sn19.10:1.4"
msgid "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti virājenti. "
msgstr "Vultures, crows, and hawks kept chasing him, pecking, plucking, and hacking "

msgctxt "sn19.10:1.5"
msgid "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … "
msgstr "as he screamed in pain. …” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn19.10:1.6"
msgid "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe gāmakūṭako ahosi … pe …. "
msgstr "“That being used to be a corrupt official right here in Rājagaha. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.10:1.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn19.10:1.8"
msgid "Paṭhamo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.1"
msgid "Aṭṭhi pesi ubho gāvaghātakā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.2"
msgid "Piṇḍo sākuṇiyo nicchavorabbhi; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.3"
msgid "Asi sūkariko sattimāgavi, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.4"
msgid "Usu kāraṇiko sūci sārathi; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.5"
msgid "Yo ca sibbiyati sūcako hi so, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn19.10:2.6"
msgid "Aṇḍabhāri ahu gāmakūṭakoti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
